span><hr size=1> Read today's patch message.<br>
<br>
The minimum faction message needed to do the armor quests in Kael and Skyshrine (but not Thurgadin, 'cos the Thurgadin armor is largely junk) has been raised to &quot;allied&quot;, which is a new faction category above &quot;warmly&quot;.<br>
<br>
According to the patch message, allied is &quot;SIGNIFICANTLY&quot; higher than warmly, whatever that means.<br>
<br>
Looks like a few weeks more of Dorf Kiting or Giant-Slaughtering for anyone who still wants to bother.<br>
<br>
God I am sick of faction work.<br>
